  "normal_outcomes": [
    {
      "code": "CTRL",
      "name": "拿捏者",
      "one_liner": "人形自走任务管理器",
      "pattern": "HHH-HMH-MHH-HHH-MHM",
      "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/serenakeyitan/sbti-wiki/main/images/CTRL.png",
      "rarity": {
        "percent": 3.61,
        "label": "中等",
        "one_in_x": 28
      },
      "is_special": false,
      "commentary": "高自信、高清晰度、高价值、高责任、高行动力，几乎全 H。作者把 CTRL 当成\"完美体\"在写，基本是测试里最卷最能搞事情的人。现实里对应的是那种\"你塌方了，他一个信息把你拽回来\"的朋友。"
    },
    {
      "code": "ATM-er",
      "name": "送钱者",
      "one_liner": "永远在支付时间、精力、耐心",
      "pattern": "HHH-HHM-HHH-HMH-MHL",
      "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/serenakeyitan/sbti-wiki/main/images/ATM-er.png",
      "rarity": {
        "percent": 2.46,
        "label": "中等",
        "one_in_x": 41
      },
      "is_special": false,
      "commentary": "和 CTRL 几乎像孪生，但最后一栏 So1/So2/So3 是 M-H-L——社交主动性中等、边界感偏强但表达真实度低。简单说就是\"什么都扛，但从来不说累\"的那种人。"
    },
    {
      "code": "Dior-s",
      "name": "屌丝",
      "one_liner": "第欧根尼的精神传人",
      "pattern": "MHM-MMH-MHM-HMH-LHL",
      "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/serenakeyitan/sbti-wiki/main/images/Dior-s.jpg",
      "rarity": {
        "percent": 5.23,
        "label": "较常见",
        "one_in_x": 19
      },
      "is_special": false,
      "commentary": "名字玩谐音梗：Diogenes' Original Realist - sage（犬儒主义先贤）。整体 M/H 为主，没有特别低的项，是一种\"看破红尘但过得挺舒服\"的躺平老哲人，和字面\"屌丝\"没什么关系。"
    },
    {
      "code": "BOSS",
      "name": "领导者",
      "one_liner": "手里永远拿着方向盘的人",
      "pattern": "HHH-HMH-MMH-HHH-LHL",
      "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/serenakeyitan/sbti-wiki/main/images/BOSS.png",
      "rarity": {
        "percent": 1.53,
        "label": "稀有",
        "one_in_x": 65
      },
      "is_special": false,
      "commentary": "除了社交那一组偏低，其他全是 H。典型的\"事业狂 + 秩序控\"，对别人和自己都狠，最容易出现在高强度职场环境里。"
    },
    {
      "code": "THAN-K",
      "name": "感恩者",
      "one_liner": "永不枯竭的正能量发射塔",
      "pattern": "MHM-HMM-HHM-MMH-MHL",
      "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/serenakeyitan/sbti-wiki/main/images/THAN-K.png",
      "rarity": {
        "percent": 7.76,
        "label": "较常见",
        "one_in_x": 13
      },
      "is_special": false,
      "commentary": "情感投入度和世界观倾向都偏 H，但边界和执行偏 M。就是那种认真相信\"凡事皆有其意义\"的朋友，真诚到让人一时反应不过来。"
    },
    {
      "code": "OH-NO",
      "name": "哦不人",
      "one_liner": "一声\"Oh no!\"把风险扼杀在萌芽",
      "pattern": "HHL-LMH-LHH-HHM-LHL",
      "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/serenakeyitan/sbti-wiki/main/images/OH-NO.png",
      "rarity": {
        "percent": 3.05,
        "label": "中等",
        "one_in_x": 33
      },
      "is_special": false,
      "commentary": "高自我清晰度 + 极强的秩序感 + 高边界感，但依恋安全感 L、社交主动性 L。一个词：控场型秩序守护神，对\"失控\"的容忍度接近 0。"
    },
    {
      "code": "GOGO",
      "name": "行者",
      "one_liner": "世界只有已完成和即将被完成",
      "pattern": "HHM-HMH-MMH-HHH-MHM",
      "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/serenakeyitan/sbti-wiki/main/images/GOGO.png",
      "rarity": {
        "percent": 3.05,
        "label": "中等",
        "one_in_x": 33
      },
      "is_special": false,
      "commentary": "和 CTRL 非常接近，但 S3 核心价值是 M 而不是 H，So1 主动性也略低。差别在于：CTRL 在拿捏别人，GOGO 在拿捏自己的 todo list，目标更\"所见即所得\"。"
    },
    {
